ed="T" n="0830a09"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0830a09"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName><persName key="A012330">安靜</persName>傳（<persName key="A012333">徐果師</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0830a10"/><persName key="A012330">釋安靜</persName>，本<placeName key="PL000000055436">西域</placeName>人也。<date from-iso="+0727-01-31" key="j19866211987004" to-iso="+0728-02-18"><name>開元</name>十五年</date>振錫東遊，<lb
ed="T" n="0830a11"/>至<placeName key="PL000000023000">定陶</placeName>，直問：「<persName key="A012331">丁<roleName>居士</roleName></persName>何在？」鄉人報之曰：「終<lb
ed="T" n="0830a12"/>已三載，葬在郊外。」且曰：「是人也乃在家菩薩，<lb
ed="T" n="0830a13"/>專勤<name>梵</name>行，甞<anchor xml:id="beg0830sgsz1"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0830sgsz1"/>事<placeName key="PL000000023253">嵩山</placeName><persName key="A009319">普寂<roleName>禪師</roleName></persName>，云已得<lb
ed="T" n="0830a14"/>甚深法。將終，合掌加趺而坐，儼然而絕。<placeName key="PL000000023000">曹城</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0830a15"/>諸寺院鐘磬不擊自鳴也。」<persName key="A012330">靜</persName>至墳所，躬自發<lb
ed="T" n="0830a16"/>之。時五色雲氣騰噴而上，遂取其骨──皆金<lb
ed="T" n="0830a17"/>色，連環<anchor xml:id="beg0830sgsz3"/>若<anchor xml:id="end0830sgsz3"/>鎖，可五丈許──，鏗然響亮，擐杖頭<lb
ed="T" n="0830a18"/>而行。別樹塔重葬，眾咸驚<anchor xml:id="beg0830sgsz5"/>歎<anchor xml:id="end0830sgsz5"/>。少頃，<persName key="A012330">靜</persName>瞥然滅<lb
ed="T" n="0830a19"/>沒焉。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0830a2001"><lb
ed="T" n="0830a20"/>系曰：有情<ptr type="glossary" target="#g826"/>遺骼，引因<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1700"/><anchor xml:id="beg0830001"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>踐</sic><corr>殘</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0830001"/>果<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1701"/>也。凡夫身中節<lb
ed="T" n="0830a21"/>不相至，十地菩薩骨節解盤龍相結<ptr target="#n2484"/>，佛則全<lb
ed="T" n="0830a22"/>身舍利焉。今<persName key="A012331">丁<roleName>居士</roleName></persName>骨有鉤鎖形，則超凡<lb
ed="T" n="0830a23"/>夫，未階十<anchor xml:id="beg0830sgsz7"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>在</sic><corr>住</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0830sgsz7"/>，此乃八臂<persName key="A018994">那羅延</persName>身骨節頭<lb
ed="T" n="0830a24"/>相鉤是歟？證居士力量及此矣。譬若出金<lb
ed="T" n="0830a25"/>之砂之謂渾，不可謂為砂也；含玉之石之<lb
ed="T" n="0830a26"/>謂璞，不可謂為石也矣。</p><p xml:id="pT50p0830a2701"><lb
ed="T" n="0830a27"/>次又<placeName key="PL000000058938"><placeName>成都府</placeName><placeName>大雲寺</placeName></placeName>有<persName key="A012333">徐果<roleName>師</roleName></persName>者，混物韜<lb
ed="T" n="0830a28"/>光，人罕詳測。或入三昧，不失律儀。或示<lb
ed="T" n="0830a29"/>狂癡，語事多中。先為<persName key="A006551">衛元嵩</persName>，是難測之士，<pb ed="T" n="0830b" xml:id="T50.2061.0830b"/><lb
    ed="T" n="0830b01"/>坤維<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1492"/>間往往有人謂之<persName key="A012333">徐果<roleName>師</roleName></persName>。<name>徐</name>，姓也；<name>果</name>，名<lb
ed="T" n="0830b02"/>也；師，通稱也。此亦<persName key="A005932">彊練</persName>、<persName key="A002296">誌<roleName>公</roleName></persName>之倫類矣，不知<lb
ed="T" n="0830b03"/>其終云。</p>
